<item>
            <title>[LU-422] broken lines need to be terminated with continuation markers in extract_patches</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-422</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In commit fb7a499bf47530b9eee162990c8f1815b643d30e there was a sed introduced that was broken across several lines with no line continuations:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;		ver=$(echo $ver |&lt;br/&gt;
		  sed -e &apos;s/^v&amp;#40;.*&amp;#41;/\1/&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
		      -e &apos;s/_RC&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0-9&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.*$//&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
		      -e &apos;s/_/./g&apos;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is, of course, incorrect.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
